thank you for all the love on my new single daylight, this release has been the most exciting for me yet. moments like these are when i reflect on how i didn't quit doing what i love despite what everybody else was saying in my life, if you see it just go for it. i am just grateful to do what i love most by making the world a better place one song at a time. i still can't wrap my head around how much you guys love daylight. thank you for everything from the bottom of my heart, all of you mean so much to me.

my first north american tour is almost over, i'm getting sad but its bittersweet. i am so thankful for all who have came to the shows thus far! also, make sure to checkout my new single 'Dead Man' love u <33

20 shows down. 3 more to go. i'm soaking it all in. words can't describe how grateful i am to be here in this present moment doing what i am doing. this wouldn't be possible without all you beautiful people, the fans. this is just the beginning <3

-dk

my first north american tour has ended. 23 unforgettable shows just like that. i've struggled to comprehend what has accumulated this past year for me, words will never be able to possibly describe what you all mean to me. theres moments the pressure is unbearable and it's hard to live in the present all the time. what i get to do because of you beautiful people will never feel real to me, it's truly a blessing. thank you to everyone involved for an unbelievable first tour, i can't wrap my head around the fact that this is just the beginning <3

-dk
